      • request

        public void request(java.lang.String url,
                    java.lang.String cachePath,
                    java.lang.Object tag)
        Sends the request to the specified URL and with the specified caching path
        Parameters:
        url - The URL to send the request to
        cachePath - The path at which to store the cached version of this request. If the path is null, the request wont be cached.
        tag - A custom object that will be passed in the delegate methods of this request (nullable)
